# Public site URL — no trailing slash. Set in Vercel → Environment Variables → Production (and optional .env.local).
# Required for correct canonical URLs, sitemap, JSON-LD, and social previews (WhatsApp / LinkedIn read absolute og:url and og:image).
# Current production:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://umer-sheraz-portfolio.vercel.app
#
# If you add a custom domain, use that URL instead and redeploy.
#
# Share preview image: place your headshot at public/profile.png (path must match src/content/site.ts → site.photo.src).
